author: Second Wind
description:
KC and Marty are preparing themselves for Metroid Prime 4: Beyond by jamming through a bunch of Metroid games. This time, they're hopping into 2021's Metroid Dread.

If you dig watching us play through these full series of games, considering supporting us over at Patreon -- https://www.patreon.com/SecondWindGroup

title: Starting Metroid Dread for the First Time w/ KC and Marty - Part 1
